<plot>Alex is finally having a romantic evening with his girlfriend. But just as their evening is about to climax, his best friend Michael arrives to borrow Alex's razor. With the night already in shambles, Alex finally decides to put an end to Michael's intrusive and selfish behavior. On this one night, the boundaries of their friendship will be tested.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?080728</url></doc>
